{"tid":1676960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［忽發奇想新職業］點令黃店小店增加客流？","createTime":"2019-10-26T18:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T00:35:15.000Z","uid":296536,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"107f842a618a0daa1a2337d7df0d8a9eb7dff03f","tid":1676960,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:32:57.000Z","msg":"P 牌冇得推，覺得有得諗嘅就幫推＋討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話黃色經濟圈，成日就係聽到幾間大店比人懲罰，雖然話有一班人係為打卡，但係最大問題係<span style=\"color: red;\">留意唔到有咩小店要幫</span>，其實係咪可以新增一個職業<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班馬師</span></span>，搵人響唔同街道同商場（樓上舖就要再諗，好似難啲做）定時巡邏，睇下黃店內人流情況，再update一個status 呢, 我諗法就係ride on而家嘅藍黃店app/page，即時refresh 比大家睇個情況, 再狗衝去缺人嘅黃店。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(1)點介定人流情況？</span><br />\n大概分幾支顏色嘅Flag, 代表&quot;冇人啊屌/小貓三兩隻/坐得一半咋要人/差幾個就full/滿座/長龍狀態&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(2)冇錢收搵鬼做咩？</span><br />\n其實呢個方法行得通嘅話，經濟效益會幾大，改善食店嘅人流分配，所以眾籌請人做啦，請人派傳單都要錢啦，夾啲錢做啲大效益過派傳單嘅野正常不過姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長遠黎講，做得掂嘅話係黃店老闆出錢請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(3)即係搵咩人做？</span><br />\n好多手足已經為左場運動傾家蕩產啦，好多小朋友都話冇錢食飯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就一於創造下就業職位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚直接收錢唔好意思，咁打工出糧都好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(4)點巡法姐？由日巡到黑咩？</span><br />\n靈活分更表，我諗法就係Weekdays peak hours (0730-0900,1200-1330,1800-2200)+ weekend 全日, 可以試行一啲區域先，ok嘅話就擴展到18區。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(5)好似好大陣象Wor？</span><br />\n其實諗過可唔可以由普通顧客，甚至同黃店員工合作，由佢地Update status，但諗到好易比有心人亂update，同埋好難叫哂全部小店員工跟住做，所以請班<span style=\"color: red;\">班馬專員</span>做準確啲效率高啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(6)知左邊間小店冇人又點？啲人都係去哂名店打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n係，個個去為打卡咁真係冇用，但我相信總會有人目標係做到全部黃店生意興隆開分店，所以夠多人做嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">係可以將呢樣野變做一個潮流</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟對黃色經濟圈好有興趣，一路都諗點樣可以實踐出黎，同埋長遠擴大個規模，爭取響社會上嘅話語權，希望大家唔介意我P牌交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7514aa070b2766b3a0dfc919c6150c7f0d01dc1","tid":1676960,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210cc840f73caf5c1b3e3ebdaad7ec425a8ab763","tid":1676960,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z50G3y8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz50G3y8.jpg&h=1506bd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5r3xsv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5r3xsv.gif&h=6d533f2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1ff90ce4dc808e8a518a0e13cf8b773e5f26382","tid":1676960,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"無力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a6b98a34639148f95c81bd88101f358a595326","tid":1676960,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbMZP3J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbMZP3J.gif&h=805767b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8398483e0092b45c76367ae45227011dfff20b8f","tid":1676960,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:45:31.000Z","msg":"係長龍黃店門口貼附近黃店List/地圖有冇得諗？<br />\n堅黃店應該唔介意，排緊隊既又可以知附近仲有咩選擇<br />\n慢慢散開去"},{"pid":"04d046200fd83bcbcdbf7a4dfec79e93b0e74436","tid":1676960,